ZH: 流感是一种呼吸道传染病。
EN: Influenza is a respiratory infectious disease.

ZH: 我昨天感到头痛和发烧，可能是流感。
EN: I felt headache and fever yesterday, maybe it's flu.

ZH: 流感疫苗可以帮助我们预防这种疾病。
EN: Influenza vaccine can help us prevent this disease.

ZH: 流感病毒会在冬季传播得更快。
EN: The flu virus spreads faster in winter.

ZH: 流感病毒可以通过咳嗽或打喷嚏传播。
EN: The flu virus can be transmitted through coughing or sneezing.

ZH: 我的同事得了流感，所以我决定戴口罩。
EN: My colleague has the flu, so I decided to wear a mask.

ZH: 流感症状包括咳嗽、打喷嚏和喉咙痛。
EN: Symptoms of influenza include coughing, sneezing, and sore throat.

ZH: 流感可以引起严重的并发症。
EN: Influenza can cause serious complications.

ZH: 我每年都会接种流感疫苗。
EN: I get vaccinated against the flu every year.

ZH: 流感的传播速度非常迅速。
EN: The transmission rate of flu is very fast.

ZH: 流感对老年人和儿童尤其危险。
EN: Influenza is particularly dangerous for the elderly and children.

ZH: 我的朋友昨天被确诊患有流感。
EN: My friend was diagnosed with flu yesterday.

ZH: 流感可以让人感到非常虚弱和疲惫。
EN: Influenza can make people feel very weak and tired.

ZH: 你最好多喝水，因为你有可能得了流感。
EN: You should drink more water, because you might have flu.

ZH: 流感季节到了，大家都要注意保暖。
EN: The flu season is here, everyone should keep warm.

ZH: 流感是一种常见的传染病。
EN: Influenza is a common infectious disease.

ZH: 我希望今年不要得流感。
EN: I hope I won't get the flu this year.

ZH: 流感病毒的变异能力很强。
EN: The influenza virus has a strong ability to mutate.

ZH: 流感疫苗有助于减少疾病传播。
EN: Influenza vaccine helps reduce the spread of the disease.
